subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Tenth-seeded Serena Williams rallied from a break down in both sets to beat Samantha Stosur, 7-5, 6-3, and advanced to the quarterfinals of the Sony Ericsson Open in Key Biscayne, Fla.
